  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Train 100 men &amp; 40 boys in Uganda on menstruation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will engage/train 100 men including district policymakers, traditional cultural &amp; religious leaders, sector/departmental heads and 40 boys on menstruation management as sexual reproductive health &amp; its importance to girls education in Buvuma Islands by June 2020. This will increase their knowledge, attitude &amp; practice on menstruation thus increased access to hygienic menstrual materials, scholastic materials that&apos;ll reduce school absenteeism, dropout, child marriage &amp; pregnancies.</narrative>
  </description>
